523
00:38:30.790 --> 00:38:33.700
Vuoi un'altra coca?

524
00:38:33.790 --> 00:38:34.870
Okay.

525
00:38:35.990 --> 00:38:39.490
- Ancora due coca.
- Due coca.


526
00:38:39.580 --> 00:38:42.990
